This test case demonstrates the delete by Primary Key Option of the program
The delete by Primary Key is executed with menu option 'd/D' option

This test case consists of:
   TC1. Delete by Primary Key on Empty Database   =>  Not found 
   TC2. Delete by Primary Key on Populated Databse => Use search by primary key to prove the movie is deleted 
   TC3. Delete by an incorrect Primary Key on Populated Database = > Not found
